thread.title: MW

author: MW
title: MW
text: This review is for my second DY bracelet I have purchased from this site. The first one was rated in "excellent" condition and this one was rated in "good" condition. Definitely a difference in shine on the tiny gold section of the bracelet, however the price was $250 dollars below retail. I knew from the pictures I was making a choice between extra shine on a small section and the money. The bracelet is wonderful, and I was able to save some money!!
